  "text": "The negatively oriented entities of contact S and others on this planet are limited by the first distortion. They have obviously been limited by the vanishing ritual just performed. Could you describe with respect to free will, how they limit themselves in order to work within the first distortion, and how the banishing ritual itself is this query has several portions. Whenever they feel it possible, secondly they are limited by the great law of confusion in that for the most part, they are unable to enter this planetary sphere of influence, and are able to use the windows of time, a space, a distortion only in so far as there is some calling to balance the positive calling. A physical complex of its free will. Thus a terrier has been automated.",
